title: Rocket Player Premium Unlocker 1.1.1
description:
A music player designed with both the easy and advanced music listener in mind. The Premium Unlocker unlocks advanced features built on top of the easy to use interface of the free music player.
This premium unlocker unlocks the following features in Rocket Player:

- Support for even more audio formats: Apple Lossless (alac), True Audio (tta), APE (ape), Musepack (mpc),Waveform Audio File (wav), Free Lossless Audio Codec (flac), WavePack (wv) and Windows Media Audio (except lossless and copy protected) (wma)
- Premium themes
- 10 band graphic equalizer
- Assign an equalizer preset to a song, genre, playlist, artist, album, or podcast
- Preamp
- Limiter
- Right/Left balance control
- Gapless playback
- Variable playback speed for podcasts
- Variable playback speed for music
- Replay gain
- Crossfading
